# Fix Banner Image Paths

The banner images are not appearing because the frontend is using relative paths (e.g., `images/banners/banner1.jpg`) from the database without prepending the required base URL (`https://frame9.my/uploads/`).

## Proposed Changes

### [Component Name]

#### [MODIFY] [constants.ts](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/frame9/src/constants.ts)
- Add `IMAGE_BASE_URL` constant set to `https://frame9.my/uploads/`.

#### [MODIFY] [Home.vue](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/frame9/src/screens/Home.vue)
- Import `IMAGE_BASE_URL`.
- Update the `banners` computed property to prepend the base URL to each image path.

